org.eclipse.jetty.util.ajax

Interface JSON.Convertor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JSONCollectionConvertor, JSONDateConvertor, JSONEnumConvertor, JSONObjectConvertor, JSONPojoConvertor, JSONPojoConvertorFactory
    Enclosing class:
    JSON

    public static interface JSON.Convertor
    Static JSON Convertor.

    may be implemented to provide static convertors for objects that may be registered with JSON.registerConvertor(Class, org.eclipse.jetty.util.ajax.JSON.Convertor) . These convertors are looked up by class, interface and super class by JSON.getConvertor(Class). Convertors should be used when the classes to be converted cannot implement JSON.Convertible or JSON.Generator.
